        {
            "title": "康怡戲院開幕38年月底結業  區內市民呻可惜不捨：同戲院一齊大",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"康怡戲院開幕38年月底結業 區內市民呻可惜不捨：同戲院一齊大\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/e071c9049707abeadfc1022a62770c15/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250515/_2025051522502297403.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">康怡戲院開幕38年月底結業 區內市民呻可惜不捨：同戲院一齊大</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>康怡戲院將於月底結業，為今年第3間戲院結業。《星島頭條》記者晚上9時半到戲院觀察，戲院售票處外貼出告示指，由於租約期滿，戲院將於本月28日起結業，感謝街坊多年支持。戲院1987年開幕至今38年，是區內街坊集體回憶，有市民在告示前「打卡」留念。與太太到戲院觀看港產片《送院途中》的方先生表示，於區內居住40多年，與戲院一同成長，對其結業感可惜，「與女友交往時來這裡看電影，小朋友出世後又帶他們來看動畫。」\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4251048/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"與太太到戲院觀看港產片《送院途中》的方先生。劉駿軒攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1ed64351a32032d7556cf6a0514f3dae/2025-05/435345.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        與太太到戲院觀看港產片《送院途中》的方先生。劉駿軒攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4251037/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"康怡戲院將於月底結業，為今年第3間戲院結業。劉駿軒攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/41c970c996ed1773fe805711d89136ca/2025-05/0987490964804964.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        康怡戲院將於月底結業，為今年第3間戲院結業。劉駿軒攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4251038/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"《星島頭條》記者晚上9時半到戲院觀察。劉駿軒攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4ce75be7ff9f569b5b5714145e361b90/2025-05/86048606046048.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        《星島頭條》記者晚上9時半到戲院觀察。劉駿軒攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4251039/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"戲院售票處外貼出告示指，由於租約期滿，戲院將於本月28日起結業。劉駿軒攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/35dcbae461ac5a51427b383b250c7b9e/2025-05/7980798684.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        戲院售票處外貼出告示指，由於租約期滿，戲院將於本月28日起結業。劉駿軒攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4251040/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"戲院售票處外貼出告示指，由於租約期滿，戲院將於本月28日起結業。劉駿軒攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/bb062cd4f56aaef4a49d799707579f59/2025-05/0976564909.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        戲院售票處外貼出告示指，由於租約期滿，戲院將於本月28日起結業。劉駿軒攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4251041/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"戲院售票處外貼出告示指，由於租約期滿，戲院將於本月28日起結業。劉駿軒攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b8d4a1e8d834fcc7241cea2000b81d9b/2025-05/09876.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        戲院售票處外貼出告示指，由於租約期滿，戲院將於本月28日起結業。劉駿軒攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>康怡戲院結業後，港島東只剩3間戲院，包括位於太古的「百老匯 MOViE MOViE Pacific Place」、位於筲箕灣的「嘉禾 銀河廣場」，以及位於柴灣的「Cinema City 柴灣」。方先生指，康怡戲院位置方便，較易買票，價錢僅銅鑼灣一帶戲院的「七、八折」，對港島東戲院減少感「頭痛」，「若太古城沒有播映想看的電影，或沒有適合的場次，就會不知所措。」 \n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4251046/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"戲院1987年開幕至今38年，是區內街坊集體回憶。劉駿軒攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/54d883d6e1f3be1653d21517787b1860/2025-05/896040840.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        戲院1987年開幕至今38年，是區內街坊集體回憶。劉駿軒攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4251042/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"戲院1987年開幕至今38年，是區內街坊集體回憶。劉駿軒攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d0f72b5fb90a0756a12ce806385d2e72/2025-05/86046504.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        戲院1987年開幕至今38年，是區內街坊集體回憶。劉駿軒攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4251043/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"戲院1987年開幕至今38年，是區內街坊集體回憶。劉駿軒攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/681c4dc08789129d895a2226b49941e2/2025-05/8648648648.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        戲院1987年開幕至今38年，是區內街坊集體回憶。劉駿軒攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4251044/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"康怡戲院結業後，港島東只剩3間戲院。劉駿軒攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/94e206cb464b098e60b38f353b09adae/2025-05/808008084668904.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        康怡戲院結業後，港島東只剩3間戲院。劉駿軒攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4251045/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"康怡戲院結業後，港島東只剩3間戲院。劉駿軒攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7ca3ec1420c480e283dc22599e8b275b/2025-05/8468496896048964.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        康怡戲院結業後，港島東只剩3間戲院。劉駿軒攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>另一街坊區小姐表示，自己於附近居住近30年，對區內戲院結業感可惜，「因為都住了很久，見證了戲院存在很久。如果想看電影，就會在這裡看。」她指，未來會轉到太古城看電影。\n\n</p>\n<p>記者 蕭博禧\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
